snippet: Michael Schumacher's management has warned that someone is trying to sell documents that may be the medical files of the seven-time Formula One world champion....

headline.print_headline: Schumacher's Medical Files Might Have Been Stolen
headline.main: Schumacher's Medical Files Might Have Been Stolen

lead_paragraph: Michael Schumacher's management has warned that someone is trying to sell documents that may be the medical files of the seven-time Formula One world champion.
